title: #92Noon at the Fair! Charch/Saunders/Gleeman
description: The #FaithFamily is live for its final fair appearance of the year. Charch joins for the entirety of the show. Wolves Head Coach, Ryan Saunders, stops by. And a visit from resident techie, Aaron Gleeman, for some Twins talk.
